Package org.neo4j.index.internal.gbptree

Interface OffloadStore<KEY,​VALUE>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OffloadStoreImpl
    public interface OffloadStore<KEY,​VALUE>
    Store used by TreeNodeDynamicSize to store keys and values that are too large to be inlined in GBPTree.

      • writeKeyValue

        long writeKeyValue​(KEY key,
                   VALUE value,
                   long stableGeneration,
                   long unstableGeneration,
                   PageCursorTracer cursorTracer)
            throws IOException
        Store key and value in offload store, mapping them to offloadId that can be used when reading the key and value back.
        Parameters:
        key - the key to write to offload store.
        value - the value to write to offload store together with key.
        stableGeneration - current stable generation when key is written.
        unstableGeneration - current unstable generation when key is written.
        cursorTracer - underlying page cursor tracer
        Returns:
        offloadId to use when reading key and value back.
        Throws:
        IOException - if something went wrong while writing key or value.
